            <div class="breakdown-row"><span>− 純有利子負債</span><span class="val neg" id="m_debt2_disp">—</span></div>
            <div class="breakdown-row total"><span>株式価値（買収価格目安）</span><span class="val" id="m_equity2_disp">—</span></div>
